          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "荣耀盼望是基督，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "祂是神的奥秘；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "使我有分神丰满，"
